nce; Google will notice it.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:13.3333px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">&middot;</span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,\"><span style=\"color:black\">Useful formatting--</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;Google will be more likely to display your content if it is well formatted.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:13.3333px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">&middot;</span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,\"><span style=\"color:black\">Don&rsquo;t forget SEO--</span></span></span></strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,\"><span style=\"color:#243838\">If your content isn&rsquo;t good enough to reach page one, it won&rsquo;t make position zero.</span></span></span></span><strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,\"><span style=\"color:black\">It includes on site as well-Off site SEO.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:13.3333px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"color:black\">&middot